public
pull_request: activity on a pull request in the workflow's repository occurs.
     _comment (use issue_comment): comment on a pr is created
     _review: review is submitted, edited, or dismissed
     _review_comment: review comment is modified. 
     _target: 
push:  push a commit or tag.
release:  release activity in your repository occurs.

repository_dispatch: activity that happens outside of GitHub.

schedule: trigger a workflow at a scheduled time.

status: status of a Git commit changes.

workflow_dispatch: manually triggered a workflow.
workflow_call: called by another workflow.
workflow_run: another workflow run is [completed, requested, in_progress] 
